WEBVTT

00:03:28.957 --> 00:03:30.783
how we encourage people to study,

00:03:30.807 --> 00:03:32.730
our jokes, our codes ...

00:03:32.754 --> 00:03:35.701
And it ultimately determines
how innovative we can be.

00:03:36.503 --> 00:03:40.510
So, that's the first reason
we don't innovate in sanitation.

00:03:41.079 --> 00:03:44.392
We're kind of uncomfortable
talking about sanitation,

00:03:44.416 --> 00:03:47.118
that's why I've gotten called
"The Poo Princess" so much.

00:03:47.142 --> 00:03:48.833
The second reason is:

00:03:48.857 --> 00:03:51.387
we think the problem is solved
here in the US.

00:03:51.833 --> 00:03:53.063
But not so.

00:03:53.087 --> 00:03:58.129
